<p class="govuk-body">Use this component to introduce content that has force of law (sometimes referred to as tertiary legislation).</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">How it works</h2>


<p class="govuk-body">Where possible write force of law in plain English in collaboration with the Solicitor's Office to make sure it’s legally correct.</p>


<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Where to place this component</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Use this component just before the text that has force of law.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
Force of law text should be put at the point the user needs to know it to complete their task.
</p>


